      "message": "So, a lazy cache.  Shouldn\u0027t we make it thread safe somehow, like\n\n  public:\n    // May return nullptr if this can\u0027t be represented by an SkPath.\n    SkPath* findOrCachePath(SkScalerContext*, SkArenaAlloc*) const;\n\n  private:\n    mutable SkOnce  fPathOnce;\n    mutable SkPath* fPath;\n\n\n  SkPath* SkGlyph::findOrCachePath(SkScalerContext*, SkArenaAlloc*) const {\n      fPathOnce([\u0026] {\n         ...\n         fPath \u003d ...;\n      });\n      return fPath;\n  }\n?",
